Grounded heard Aerotaur.  "All right.  But we are not doing this to 
kill Deemos. IF, and only if, we have to kill him it must be done in 
self defense.  We also will have no arguing over who to kills him, 
like barbarians.  Aerotaur, Sarge.  You two will share leadership in 
the attack.  You will learn teamwork.  You will also both train 
Trinity, Aerotaur because you know her, and Sarge, because you 
don't. "

As Birdbot and Papertron flew in he felt the vibrations as Birdbot 
flew at Trinity and Papertron aiming at her.  With a snap of either 
wrists two whips flew out made of pure energon. One at Birdbots leg 
to try and grab it and another at the weapon Papertron was 
holding.  "Thank you for coming you two.  They are your responsibilyt 
Sarge, don't forget that."
